wdi-BM.GSR.FCTY.CD.def: Primary income payments refer to employee compensation paid to nonresident workers and investment income (payments on direct investment, portfolio investment, other investments). Data are in current U.S. dollars.
wdi-BM.GSR.FCTY.CD.name: Primary income payments
wdi-BM.GSR.FCTY.CD.source: International Monetary Fund, Balance of Payments Statistics Yearbook and data files.
